      "cause": "No device in the collected configs advertises or has an interface in 172.16.0.0/24; the network appears not to be locally attached to R1 or R3, so the static/next-hop entries point at each other instead of an actual next-hop delivering the host 172.16.0.12.",
      "evidence": [
